column5: With the PC getting loaded up and space getting short,I am saving them on a wd storage unit.  Brought back some memories doing so. Thought I would share some.  Bring on the warmer weather. And the bugs. LOL
I remember some of them  I was LMAO with you and the snow traveler. it was a great idea bud.
Is that Blair with a centrepin??? LOL
Is that Blair with a centrepin??? LOL  YUUUUPPPPPPPPPPPP,he was a NATURAL.LOL
Hey Terry... what did you do with the "yoda" puller??? I could use that to pull my airplane back into the hangar!!
Hey Terry... what did you do with the "yoda" puller??? I could use that to pull my airplane back into the hangar!!   LOL Wayne.  I think the best pic is  his Martine finger..
Need to have a montage with the theme from Cheers playing. Where everybody knows your name.
Hey Terry... what did you do with the "yoda" puller??? I could use that to pull my airplane back into the hangar!! you can use it spring sommer and fall I need it for winter ice
It's winter when I need it.. damn near killed myself yesterday pulling her back in. Thought.. wonder who has an old rototiller that I could make a tailwheel puller out of...
That's a purty white Lund Ya,it,s got that nice white stripe.LOL
That's a purty white Lund  Should I be worried that I recognized the eyebrows before the boat?
Should I be worried that I recognized the eyebrows before the boat?  You looking in the mirror again?
Some nice pics!  That "snow traveler" thingy is cool.  I watched a video from Russia (?) and they all used something like that.  I think the sled was attached to the wheels though.
Great shots Brian - this year, your turn to come visit our water. See if we can't get more than 1 in the boat
You looking in the mirror again?  That must be it.
